                    </h1>
                    
                    <div class="mt-16 space-y-5 bg-[#2f2b61A6] backdrop-blur-[6px] shadow-xl rounded-[37px] w-[400px] sm:w-[500px] text-center">
                        <p class="mx-auto items-center -mx-2 font-normal text-white py-6 text-center px-24
